result.execSummary:
The defendant Matthew E Weidner was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Matthew E Weidner is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Matthew E Weidner was found guilty of Possession of Controlled Substance [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime], an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(b).
  • Matthew E Weidner was found guilty of Possession of Cocaine/Coca [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime], an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(c).
